  <brief_summary>
    <textblock>
      The purpose of this study is to assess the patient self-medication practices during and after&#xD;
      cancer in France, using an online questionnaire&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </brief_summary>
  <detailed_description>
    <textblock>
      Patients will be contacted by email from patient's associations. Patients will be informed of&#xD;
      the objectives of the study and will be free to answer or not to the online questionnaire.&#xD;
    </textblock>
  </detailed_description>
